snippet.title: Squirrelmageddon! | Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1470670/Squirrelmageddon/
Squirrelmageddon! is an indi release 3rd / 1st Person, dark humor, sci-fi, run and gun, high score squirrel wave shooter for 1-4 LAN or online players. Set in a dark future where genetically engineered Squirrels have overrun the planet, you must reclaim the earth for all humankind.

TITLE: Squirrelmageddon!
DEVELOPER: OA Games
PUBLISHER: The Streets Network
RELEASE DATE: 12 Oct, 2021
EARLY ACCESS RELEASE DATE: 2 Sep, 2021

Subscribe to our channel: https://bit.ly/2Dp0DjS
Follow Our Instagram: @insomniagimania
